-------------------------------------------------------------------
Tue Apr 14 13:28:28 UTC 2026 - Jan Engelhardt <jengelh@inai.de>

- Update to release 3.3.0
  * Add a better implementation of `IsFinite` for twisted conjugacy
    classes, double cosets, orbits of affine actions and group
    derivation images.
  * `ReidemeisterNumber` now immediately returns infinity if the
    source group is finite but the range group is infinite.

-------------------------------------------------------------------
Tue Feb 17 09:43:35 UTC 2026 - Jan Engelhardt <jengelh@inai.de>

- Update to release 3.2.0
  * Renamed many of the existing functions available for
    Reidemeister zeta functions.
  * Added support for Reidemeister generating functions.

-------------------------------------------------------------------
Wed Oct 15 10:31:26 UTC 2025 - Jan Engelhardt <jengelh@inai.de>

- Update to release 3.1.1
  * Affine actions can now be compared using the equality (=)
    operator.
  * Improvements to the documentation of derivations and affine
    actions.

